videos.description: Tar Heels' Sterling Manley denies Syracuse's Bourama Sidibe at the rim and Andrew Platek drills the 3-pointer on the other end.
videos.headline: Manley's block leads to Platek 3

videos.description: Syracuse gets the steal and Tyus Battle throws down the easy dunk on the fast break.
videos.headline: Battle goes airborne in transition

videos.description: Theo Pinson takes the ball away and makes a nice finish on the fast break for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: UNC's Pinson gets the steal and the bucket

videos.description: Luke Maye collects the defensive rebound and finds Kenny Williams streaking to the basket for the layup.
videos.headline: Maye shows off vision on nice assist

videos.description: Orange G Oshae Brissett gives Syracuse the momentum at the end of the first half with a 3-pointer to beat the buzzer.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Brissett drills buzzer-beater at the half

videos.headline: Syracuse's Howard makes a nifty assist to Brissett

videos.headline: Pinson records career-high in UNC win
